"{\"comment\":\"8. PAW LASSIE jumped well to win over the 450m at Warrnambool two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing second at this track last start. Comes through a solid form race last start. Capable of going well again. 1. PAW LUANNE failed to come into contention last start after drifting back at Sandown, but prior to that won easily by 4 lengths at Warrnambool (22.68) beating Molly Rochelle in a Maiden on April 2. Should play a prominent role. 2. TWENTY KNOTS turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at The Meadows over 525m behind Indy Melmen (30.78) in a Grade 7. Can measure up this time. 5. FLYING OFFSHORE did a good job to finish second last time out over 460m at this track (26.27) in a Rank Limit - Grade 6, the second top-three finish on the trot.\",\"runners\":[8,1,2,5],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Paul Hammon","tipRunnerNumbers":[3,4,8,5]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,3,6,5]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,4,2,7]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,5,8]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,5,3,8]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,5,8]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,4,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,1,4,5]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"GEL","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnem